            <code class="function">in int gl_VertexID;</code>
        </p></div><div class="refsect1"><a id="description"></a><h2>Description</h2><p>
            <code class="function">gl_VertexID</code> is a vertex language input variable that holds an
            integer index for the vertex. The index is impliclty generated by <code class="function">glDrawArrays</code>
            and other commands that do not reference the content of the <code class="constant">GL_ELEMENT_ARRAY_BUFFER</code>, or
            explicitly generated from the content of the <code class="constant">GL_ELEMENT_ARRAY_BUFFER</code>
            by commands such as <code class="function">glDrawElements</code>.
